            &none &bt BT_CLR &bt BT_PRV &bt BT_NXT   &bt BT_SEL 0 &bt BT_SEL 1                                     &none        &kp F7    &kp F8 &kp F9 &kp F12 &none
            &none &kp C_PREV &kp C_NEXT &kp C_VOL_DN &kp C_VOL_UP &none                                            &none        &kp F4    &kp F5 &kp F6 &kp F10 &none
            &none &none      &none      &none        &none        &none            &none    &none &none &none      &none        &kp F1    &kp F2 &kp F3 &kp F11 &none
